          "title": "Learning",
          "brief_html": "<blockquote>\n<p><strong>LEARNING OBJECTIVES</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Understand why naive $a^k \\pmod m$ overflows for large $k$.</li>\n<li>Implement square-and-multiply (binary exponentiation).</li>\n<li>Relate <code>powermod</code> to RSA encryption steps.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n"
        }
